Name: createdFromImportJournalId
Description: Gets the if of the Import that created this party.

Name: currencyCode
Description: Gets or sets the currency code.

Name: dateOfBirth
Description: Gets or sets the date of birth.

Name: deliveryTerm
Description: Gets or sets the delivery term.

Name: departmentCode
Description: Gets or sets the code of the Department this customer belongs to.

Name: discountPercent
Description: Gets or sets the fixed discount percent for this customer, this value should be between 0 and 100. Can also be used to add a premium in percent of the sales price (usually markup) by having negative number. Negative numbers can be between -1000 and 0.

Name: externalImportReference
Description: Gets or sets an external import reference that is unique within the account type (Customer, Supplier, Employee). It can be edited by any integration - at any time. Max length is 50 characters.

Name: firstName
Description: Gets or sets the first name.

Name: hourlyRate
Description: Gets or sets the hourly rate to use when billing time to the Customer.

Name: internationalIdCountryCode
Description: Gets or sets the international ID country code. Country code is given in ISO 3166-1 alfa-2 standard (Two characters).

Name: internationalIdNumber
Description: Gets or sets the international ID number. For privacy reasons queries returns 'hidden' if this field has a value and null if it's empty.

Name: internationalIdType
Description: Gets or sets the international ID type. The type is not well documented. See https://api.poweroffice.net/Web/docs/index.html#Reference/Rest/Type_Customer.md

Name: invoiceBrandingThemeCode
Description: Gets or sets the code of the BrandingTheme used when sending invoices to this customer. If NULL, the clients default branding theme will be used.

Name: lastName
Description: Gets or sets the last name.

Name: noticeOfDebtCollectionDeliveryType
Description: Gets or sets how notice of debt collection should be delivered to the customer.

Name: ourReferenceEmployeeCode
Description: Gets or sets the code of the Employee of the sales person handling this customer (Our reference).

Name: paymentTerms
Description: Gets or sets the payment terms. This is the default number of days after an invoice sent to this customer is due.

Name: reminderDeliveryType
Description: Gets or sets the how reminders should be delivered to the customer.

Name: reportInternationalId
Description: Gets or sets a value indicating whether International ID should be reported to Altinn.

Name: socialSecurityNumber
Description: Sets the social security number. For privacy reasons queries returns 'hidden' if this field has a value and null if it's empty.

Name: subledgerNumberSeriesId
Description: Sets the id to the SubledgerNumberSeries the party should be applied to when creating it.

Name: balance
Description: Property can be decimal or integer

Name: totalAmount
Description: Property can be decimal or integer
